title: Any Change?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and Elle Duncan debate if it is a big loss for the PGA Tour that Brooks Koepka is joining the LIV tour and what, if anything, does Deshaun Watson settling 20 of the 24 civil cases change for him moving forward.
